ent":["2 oz white chocolate, in pieces"]}],"id":"r310828","imageLink":"https:\/\/2.bp.blogspot.com\/-N2QT6vSVwxA\/XZWdLy5sMeI\/AAAAAAAAei8\/jdD3JIfoy60ebKNiVzW4M3Fcb1kRzwdAwCLcBGAsYHQ\/s1600\/0_CThH9HixaLl0D9pw.png","title":"Valentine's Decadent Steamed Chocolate Cake","publishedAt":"2018-02-02T00:00:00Z","nutrition":{"protein":"11 g","fat":"56 g","uom":"per 1 portion","carbohydrates":"67 g","calories":"3318 kJ \/ 793 kcal"},"usefulItems":"icing spatula, Thermomix® heart-shaped silicone cake mold, serving plate, refrigerator","hintsAndTricks":["If Thermomix® heart-shaped cake mold is unavailable, ensure the mold you're using fits into Varoma dish and Varoma lid closes properly.","Decorate cake as desired without using the white chocolate heart component.","To bake in the oven: transfer batter into prepared mold and place in a round baking dish (approx. 10 in.). Carefully fill baking dish with 2 cups water. Cover with foil. Poke a few holes in the foil to vent and bake for 25 minutes (325°F) or until center rises and is set."],"basicInfo":["easy","15m","1h 10m","4 portions"]}